<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Nserror on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/nserror/</link><description>Recent content in Nserror on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/nserror/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>NSError domain error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/objective-c/nserror/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/objective-c/nserror/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;NSError&lt;/code&gt; is an object that represents an error condition, including the domain (error category), code, and user info. Methods use &lt;code&gt;NSError **&lt;/code&gt; parameters to report errors back to callers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network operations failing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;File I/O errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid user input&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;System resource unavailability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-objc" data-lang="objc"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Not checking NSError
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSError &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;error;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSString &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;content &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [NSString stringWithContentsOfFile:&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;@&amp;#34;file.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; encoding:NSUTF8StringEncoding
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; error:&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;error];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// content may be nil, error not checked
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Always check error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSError &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;error;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSString &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;content &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [NSString stringWithContentsOfFile:&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;@&amp;#34;file.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; encoding:NSUTF8StringEncoding
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; error:&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;error];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (error) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; NSLog(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;@&amp;#34;Error: %@&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, error.localizedDescription);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-objc" data-lang="objc"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Ignoring error in network request
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSURLSessionDataTask &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;task &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [session dataTaskWithURL:url
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; completionHandler:&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;^&lt;/span&gt;(NSData &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;data, NSURLResponse &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;response, NSError &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;error) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// error not checked
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Check error in completion handler
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSURLSessionDataTask &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;task &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [session dataTaskWithURL:url
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; completionHandler:&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;^&lt;/span&gt;(NSData &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;data, NSURLResponse &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;response, NSError &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;error) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (error) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; NSLog(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;@&amp;#34;Network error: %@&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, error.localizedDescription);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// process data
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-objc" data-lang="objc"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: File not found
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSError &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;error;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSString &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;content &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [NSString stringWithContentsOfFile:&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;@&amp;#34;missing.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; encoding:NSUTF8StringEncoding
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; error:&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;error];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Error domain: NSCocoaErrorDomain, code: 260
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Network error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSURLSessionDataTask &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;task &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [session dataTaskWithURL:url
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; completionHandler:&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;^&lt;/span&gt;(NSData &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;data, NSURLResponse &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;response, NSError &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;error) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// error.domain = NSURLErrorDomain
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: JSON parse error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSError &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;error;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSDictionary &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;json &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [NSJSONSerialization JSONObjectWithData:data
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; options:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; error:&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;error];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// error if data is not valid JSON
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/objective-c/unrecognized-selector"&gt;unrecognized selector sent to instance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/objective-c/exc-bad-access"&gt;EXC_BAD_ACCESS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>